                                    children: "This is a fundamental misalignment of incentives. Lead aggregators sell volume, not intent. They want a homeowner's contact information distributed to as many buyers as possible to maximize their revenue per submit. Your goal, inversely, is exclusive, high-intent traffic ready to convert at your standard margins without a race to the bottom."
